Subject: [PATCH] fix(ci): Install package in editable mode before running
 tests

Fix ModuleNotFoundError in CI by adding 'pip install -e .' step.

This ensures pytest can import local modules (agents, engines, execution)
in the GitHub Actions environment.

Resolves: GitHub Actions run 19406075225
Fixes: #12
---
 .github/workflows/tests.yml | 3 +++
 1 file changed, 3 insertions(+)

diff --git a/.github/workflows/tests.yml b/.github/workflows/tests.yml
index 771bdbe..e94162b 100644
--- a/.github/workflows/tests.yml
+++ b/.github/workflows/tests.yml
@@ -23,5 +23,8 @@ jobs:
           python -m pip install --upgrade pip
           pip install -r requirements.txt
 
+      - name: Install package
+        run: pip install -e .
+
       - name: Run pytest
         run: pytest
